    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292650/extras/f181a20aa2bbc5ca646fef91d5422eae.avif?t=1735135889\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292650/extras_big/f181a20aa2bbc5ca646fef91d5422eae.avif?t=1735135889 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在《奇迹松鼠俱乐部》中，你可以体验到独一无二的堆叠塔防玩法，建造你的通天塔，权衡高度和炮塔性能，并应用意想不到的炮塔Build组合，轻松消灭所有敌人！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ群：996376530</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同于一般的塔防游戏，奇迹松鼠俱乐部以炮塔的堆叠和相互增益为核心策略，通过炮塔叠加和模组拼接打造高度自定义的合体塔，并享受1+1&gt;2带来的极致收益。<br>在3D立体的场景中，炮塔堆叠不仅带来了组合的自定义体验，还在高度这一维度上提供了丰富的策略和解谜体验——只有高度足够的炮塔，才能攻击到高处的敌人。而在错综复杂，崎岖陡峭，上下落差大的地图环境下，你需要珍惜所有的堆叠资源，来使得在这一维度上覆盖到更多敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292650/extras/c571a9dad1f6674026653e9371fdc79b.avif?t=1735135889\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292650/extras_big/c571a9dad1f6674026653e9371fdc79b.avif?t=1735135889 width=800 height=518 /></span></p>",
